visa_types.overview:
NOTE:
The family members listed below as identified in Article 2 of DL 30/2007 can request an appointment by email at doha.visti@esteri.it (mailto:doha.visti@esteri.it):
- spouse;
- partner in a registered partnership with the European Union citizen based on legislation of a member State, if the legislation of the host member State considers the registered partnership as equivalent to marriage and in accordance with the conditions laid down by the relevant legislation of the host Member State;
- direct descendants who are under the age of 21 or are dependent and those of the spouse or partner referred to in point (2);
- dependent direct ascendants and those of the spouse or partner referred to in (2);
- Adopting parents and adopted children and minors subject to guardianship/permanent foster care under measures issued pursuant to L. 184/83 are considered equivalent to family members referred to in points (3) and (4).
If you do not fall within any of the categories listed above, please refer back to the tourism checklist.

